OL,6,F"Things are a little bit better but
OL,7,Fit's very difficult."
OL,9,FIt comes as unpaid carers are found to
OL,10,Fsuffer poorer physical and mental
OL,11,Fhealth than non-carers and use
OL,12,Fhealthcare services more than the rest
OL,13,Fof the population, according to a new
OL,14,Freport from the Wales Networked Data
OL,15,FLaboratory (NDL).
OL,17,FThe last census in 2021 found there
OL,18,Fare more than 300,000 people in Wales
OL,19,Fwith an unpaid caring responsibility.
