OL,6,FNDL Wales, a partnership between
OL,7,FPublic Health Wales, Social Care
OL,8,FWales, Digital Health and Care Wales
OL,9,Fand Swansea University, says it is
OL,10,Fvital that unpaid carers are able to
OL,11,Faccess support and advice, both for
OL,12,Ftheir own health and wellbeing and
OL,13,Fthose they care for.
OL,15,FOne charity advocating for unpaid
OL,16,Fcarers which launched this year is
OL,17,Fcalling for local authorities across
OL,18,FWales to take a preventative stance to
OL,19,Fsupporting unpaid carers rather than
OL,20,Freacting when it's too late, leading
OL,21,Fto increased pressure on the system.
