OL,6,FDinas Powys resident Sylvia is worried
OL,7,Fabout what getting older will mean for
OL,8,Fher children's care.
OL,10,FShe says when she asked for more
OL,11,Fsupport from social services earlier
OL,12,Fthis year, she was asked to come up
OL,13,Fwith an emergency care plan - for when
OL,14,Fshe dies.
OL,16,FSylvia says that makes her feel
OL,17,F"unwanted", saying: "How would you
OL,18,Ffeel if that was said to you?
