OL,6,FIn response to Sylvia's story, a
OL,7,Fspokesperson for the Vale of Glamorgan
OL,8,FCouncil said: "Unpaid carers play a
OL,9,Fvital role in supporting their loved
OL,10,Fones and enabling them to remain in
OL,11,Ftheir homes.
OL,13,F"Where an individual consents, we
OL,14,Fundertake a carers assessment to
OL,15,Funderstand their circumstances and
OL,16,Fprovide information and support to
OL,17,Fassist them in their caring role. We
OL,18,Fwould encourage anyone in the Vale
OL,19,Fwith caring responsibilities to
OL,20,Fcontact us for such an assessment."
