OL,6,FThe council said they are "very aware"
OL,7,Fof the physically and emotionally
OL,8,Fdemanding nature of unpaid caring, and
OL,9,Fappreciate that some carers may
OL,10,Fsometimes feel they simply do not have
OL,11,Ftime to look after themselves as well.
OL,13,F"In these circumstances the council
OL,14,Fprovides a range of support for unpaid
OL,15,Fcarers, including respite packages
OL,16,Fwhere assessed as appropriate," the
OL,17,Fspokesperson said.
