OL,6,F"We have dedicated funding to pay for
OL,7,Fshort-term care and have in the past
OL,8,Fprovided respite care for Sylvia.
OL,9,FWhile we cannot commit to supporting
OL,10,Fevery request we would always
OL,11,Fencourage carers to speak to us about
OL,12,Fwhat is possible to enable them to
OL,13,Ftake a break from their caring
OL,14,Fresponsibilities."
OL,16,FThere has long been concern in the
OL,17,Fsector that if there is insufficient
OL,18,Fsupport for those providing care, the
OL,19,Fimpact on them and those they care for
OL,20,Fcould be dramatic.
