OL,6,FMike O'Brien, an unpaid carer for his
OL,7,Fparents, recently co-founded the
OL,8,Fcharitable organisation VOICES ADFOCAD
OL,9,Falongside Bobbie-Jo Haarhoff.
OL,11,FMike said: "If every unpaid carer in
OL,12,FWales decided tomorrow that they could
OL,13,Fno longer provide care then the health
OL,14,Fand social care sector would be under
OL,15,Fimmense pressure to provide the care
OL,16,Fthat we do.
