OL,4,Cwill only be available when she dies
OL,6,F"We set up the charity to raise the
OL,7,Fvoices of unpaid carers in Wales
OL,8,Fbecause quite often they are making
OL,9,Fcomplaints to councils or Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment and they're just not being
OL,11,Fheard, so we set up this organisation
OL,12,Fso they can be heard in the places
OL,13,Fthey need to be.
OL,15,F"We have Carers Rights Day and we have
OL,16,FCarers Week and the powers that be say
OL,17,Fthey're really grateful to unpaid
OL,18,Fcarers, but they need to start showing
OL,19,Fthat. They need to recognise the
OL,20,Fcontribution we make to the state."
