OL,6,FMeeting the needs of unpaid carers
OL,7,Fwill get even harder for many, with
OL,8,Fthe charity The Care Collective (TCC)
OL,9,Fannouncing in recent days it is having
OL,10,Fto permanently close down after more
OL,11,Fthan 30 years supporting unpaid carers
OL,12,Facross south Wales.
OL,14,FIt will also mean all 87 employees
OL,15,Fwill be made redundant.
OL,17,FKaren Robson, who was appointed as
OL,18,Fchief executive of TCC in June 2023,
OL,19,Fsaid: "Unfortunately, unpaid carers
OL,20,Fhave long been under-appreciated and
OL,21,Fsupport for them underfunded.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/15
