OL,6,F"I see no improvement in this
OL,7,Fsituation when organisations such as
OL,8,Fourselves are no longer able to
OL,9,Fdeliver vital services to vulnerable
OL,10,Fpeople and their carers".
OL,12,FAfter the publication of the Wales
OL,13,FNetworked Data Laboratory (NDL) report
OL,14,Fin early March, Alisha Davies, head of
OL,15,Fresearch and evaluation at Public
OL,16,FHealth Wales, said: "Understanding the
OL,17,Fsize of the unpaid carer population in
OL,18,FWales, and their needs is essential to
OL,19,Finform the support available to this
OL,20,Fvitally important population in Wales.
