OL,6,F"And yet, this is often limited by
OL,7,Fonly having one point of view: for
OL,8,Fexample, from primary care or local
OL,9,Fgovernment. Here, this new approach
OL,10,Fhas shown the value of bringing
OL,11,Fanonymous data from all parts of
OL,12,Fhealth and care systems together, to
OL,13,Fprovide a more comprehensive
OL,14,Funderstanding of unpaid carers as a
OL,15,Fgroup, and to assist agencies to
OL,16,Frespond to the needs of unpaid carers."
